## 3. ERD (텍스트 형태)

```
[UserEntity]
    id (PK)
    phoneNumber (UQ)
    status
    role
    |
    |-- 1:1 --> [ProfileEntity]
    |               id (PK)
    |               userId (FK, UQ)
    |               nickname (UQ)
    |               gender
    |               birthDate
    |               mannerScore
    |
    |-- 1:N --> [ProfileImageEntity]
    |               id (PK)
    |               userId (FK)
    |               imageUrl
    |               sortOrder
    |
    |-- 1:N --> [LikeEntity] (fromUserId)
    |               id (PK)
    |               fromUserId (FK)
    |               toUserId (FK)
    |               type (LIKE/DISLIKE/SUPER_LIKE)
    |
    |-- N:M --> [MatchEntity] (userAId, userBId)
    |               id (PK)
    |               userAId (FK)
    |               userBId (FK)
    |               |
    |               |-- 1:1 --> [ChatRoomEntity]
    |                               id (PK)
    |                               matchId (FK, UQ)
    |                               |
    |                               |-- 1:N --> [ChatMessage] (DynamoDB)
    |
    |-- 1:N --> [FollowEntity]
    |               followerId (FK)
    |               followingId (FK)
    |
    |-- 1:N --> [PostEntity]
    |               id (PK)
    |               userId (FK)
    |               |
    |               |-- 1:N --> [PostImageEntity]
    |               |-- 1:N --> [CommentEntity]
    |               |-- 1:N --> [PostLikeEntity]
    |
    |-- N:M --> [CallRoomEntity] (via CallParticipantEntity)
    |               id (PK)
    |               hostUserId (FK)
    |               |
    |               |-- 1:N --> [CallParticipantEntity]
    |                               callRoomId (FK)
    |                               userId (FK)
    |
    |-- 1:N --> [NotificationEntity]
    |-- 1:1 --> [NotificationSettingEntity]
```

